<h1 style="color:#1e1e2d; font-weight:500; margin:0;font-size:28px;">
  Reset Your Password
</h1>

<p style="color:#455056; font-size:15px;line-height:24px; margin-top:20px;">
  Use the OTP below to reset your password. This OTP is valid for 15 minutes.
</p>

<div style="margin:30px 0;">
  <span
    style="
      display:inline-block;
      padding:15px 30px;
      font-size:28px;
      letter-spacing:6px;
      font-weight:bold;
      background:#f4f4f4;
      border-radius:8px;
      color:#8b27f0;
   "
  >
    {{otp}}
  </span>
</div>

<p style="color:#999;font-size:13px;">
  If you did not request this, please ignore this email.
</p>